iche.<\/p><p>Nous sommes particuli\u00e8rement rigoureux\u00a0 dans la surveillance de notre processus de d\u00e9cision d&#8217;investissement, veillant \u00e0 ce qu&#8217;il reste \u00e0 l&#8217;abri de tout conflit d&#8217;int\u00e9r\u00eats, de d\u00e9cisions trop consensuelles (\u00ab syndrome du yes-man \u00bb), d&#8217;une d\u00e9faillance personnelle ou d&#8217;une trop forte pression administrative\/hi\u00e9rarchique.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-eedfc2c\" data-id=\"eedfc2c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67b4bf2c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"67b4bf2c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a59d370 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a59d370\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b3df65a elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"b3df65a\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inn